| Function Name             | Purpose                           |
| ------------------------- | --------------------------------- |
| `ConvertCurrency`         | Convert amount between currencies |
| `GetExchangeRate`         | Get current FX rate               |
| `RefreshExchangeRates`    | Sync/pull updated rates           |
| `CreateTransaction`       | Log a new transaction             |
| `GetTransactionByID`      | Retrieve a transaction            |
| `ListUserTransactions`    | Get user's transaction history    |
| `CancelTransaction`       | Cancel or rollback a transaction  |
| `CalculateTransactionFee` | Apply fee logic                   |
| `ApplyMarkupRate`         | Add markup to base rate           |
| `GetHistoricalRates`      | Fetch past rates (if applicable)  |
| `AnalyzeTrends`           | Provide market analysis           |
| `ValidateCurrencyCode`    | Check if currency is valid        |
